{"type": "article", "id": 3011, "title": "废弃酒瓶改造的动物台灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-23T07:28:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232936HrZDYzmIlkOySon2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t废弃的酒瓶如何处置？印度女设计师 Nishi Chauhan 想出了一个不错的法子，她将废酒瓶改造成了动物台灯，并且给这一系列贯以 Animal Farm 的名字。设计师把废酒瓶当做动物的身体，然后加上三角底座、头部等零件，接着再加入 LED 光源、电池和开关，将其变成台灯。此外设计师还对不同造型的酒瓶进行了深度加工和改造，使台灯呈现出更加可爱、亲近的形象。这一系列作品还收获了今年的<a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/en/online-exhibition/concept/?code=1193&amp;y=2014&amp;c=9&amp;a=0\" target=\"_blank\">红点概念奖项</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232934t37AkcKvf6TH8mrb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232934aWrHfEyp4bqLZ6CP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232935ieE1xDov7SNk3GRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523293595sXYwF1ZJLxSR8U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}